Class FeIscReaderTime

java.lang.Object
  de.feig.FeIscReaderTime

public class FeIscReaderTime
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the system-time in the OBID i-scan® ID ISC.LR2000, OBID i-scan® ID ISC.LRU1000/LRU2000/LRU3000.
